                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                               Blue Thunder
                               ============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(41006,255)"}               41006,x (x=1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         I cannot get this POKE to work - all it did was
                         reset the Speccy. However, I have left it here
                         in case it works for some "other" version of the
                         game.
                               Rastan.

@endnode
